016-12-19T19:46:29.000Z","msg":"含撚啦 語言同方言都分唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8690d846d3e672bcd51274e43ed67379537a438","tid":46593,"uid":20890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T19:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>on 9 分化撚.<br />\n<br />\n大撚把台灣friend</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你遇到正常台灣人咪好，但都有大把巴打遇到自大台仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無料但又要自大果下柒"},{"pid":"f5c56c6a95b270d0042c9e5b9c01921dc736884d","tid":46593,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T19:53:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講憎大陸人我應該都數一數二<br />\n但自問覺得廣東話真係唔好聽, 個人認為普通話比廣東話好聽 (口音另計)<br />\n不過我依然都係咁憎大陸人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個語言好唔好聽，口音佔多數<br />\n如果唔係點解咁多人話台灣國語好聽過中國普通話<br />\n粵語一樣，口音/腔調嘅話利君雅、王菀之同孽瘤都有分別啦<br />\n我覺得普遍嚟講香港粵語難聽在於個腔，如果成街都利君雅就咩都好聽啦，可惜香港人執腔會俾人話扮嘢"},{"pid":"14b7919f1f7068cc0de1f47aa05fa67267ebbbc7","tid":46593,"uid":9479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T19:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇一睇樓主起底&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n挑撥矛盾有乜居心？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台狗串香港人就淨係識話係挑撥 其實好多台狗本身就睇唔起香港人 睇唔起廣東話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做人唔好咁玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8005c8d887b68e7a2904db8c502f50a0f40847ba","tid":46593,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T23:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇一睇樓主起底&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n挑撥矛盾有乜居心？</blockquote><br />\n由原本出第一個post比人話無證據<br />\n所以而家拎d證明比大家睇<br />\n<br />\n利申：無PTT account"},{"pid":"17999ae3ab25aaae24e60fff4de1be4374a4bf34","tid":46593,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T23:31:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ganer: 南支那的閩南語吧 超難聽像野蠻人未開化的非洲語言 08/11 13:22<br />\n<br />\n睇嚟香港人今次真係要踏住台灣人屍體去抗蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n台語 = 台灣口音 閔南話<br />\n國語 = 台灣口音 普通話"},{"pid":"c202d238cc3e6e357b535c67b20b46c2cc581c8c","tid":46593,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T23:38:45.000Z","msg":"又玩分化<br />\n唔該其他人唔好因為呢d小事係度屌鬼<br />\n更何況同時事冇關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae50f74233e15acff6630e3fa852a48b3de392dc","tid":46593,"uid":10244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T23:50:03.000Z","msg":"又block一個"},{"pid":"9afd81e47376ad517b2871dcd00b2f86773ba306","tid":46593,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T23:51:11.000Z","msg":"請睇廣東話被食神<br />\n<br />\n有一幕<br />\n<br />\n:你up乜春呀<br />\n:閩南話<br />\n:閩南話食屎啦"},{"pid":"104c51d22ecf2c3d104423007aec6d4a63c796ea","tid":46593,"uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T23:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/075121_82e10ff96756548cf789b606d6601623.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net