=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba05a4f3961266ef28669047a3702909d6a2d8ea","tid":46593,"uid":23221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:57:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國方言數十種<br />\n湖南話、四川話這些比起其他方言更接近普通話<br />\n閩南話、廣東話、客家話偏離普通話最多<br />\n那大家公認<span style=\"color: red;\">最難聽的方言</span>是哪一種？<br />\n個人覺得是<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">廣東話</span></span>，聲調類的很生硬<br />\n所以中國流傳著一句話&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">寧願聽上海人吵架，也不願聽廣東人說話</span>&quot;<br />\n顯示上海話比較柔，因此有吳儂軟語之稱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那大家覺得最難聽的方言是哪一種？<br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n※ 發信站: 批踢踢實業坊(<a href=\"http://ptt.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fptt.cc&d=m0e3U0I%2B%2Bcs63X%2BT%2FLg42mN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=f82a04ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://ptt.cc</a>), 來自: 123.30.76.90<br />\n※ 文章網址: <a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1470839493.A.5E4.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1470839493.A.5E4.html&d=m0e3U0I%2B%2Bcs63X%2BT%2FLg42mN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=d6d5951e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1470839493.A.5E4.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛樓主死全家</span>"},{"pid":"694593cf735c27003c5ab3781ec41d870d35ada1","tid":46593,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:58:56.000Z","msg":"語言學角度"},{"pid":"6da9598c2833fdfe5622ced872874459ecc89847","tid":46593,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T01:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38o3Z59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38o3Z59.jpg&h=642feedb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開過個新ac再黎啦"},{"pid":"c3fb84f12859b22f4df8bd4f5db0204a82431b11","tid":46593,"uid":9777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T01:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/